    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧠 <strong>MOTHERBOARD UNDER ATTACK</strong> 🦠</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有电路、病毒和……焊接的塔防游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好保卫你电脑的主板吧！<br>在 <i>Motherboard Under Attack</i> 中，你将面对一波又一波试图入侵并摧毁电子元件的病毒。你的任务？在战略位置焊接元件，管理你的资源（宝贵的焊锡），并阻止病毒感染处理器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/c9d95af6b59d362c3829cd818b23afaa.poster.avif?t=1757460885\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/c9d95af6b59d362c3829cd818b23afaa.webm?t=1757460885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/c9d95af6b59d362c3829cd818b23afaa.mp4?t=1757460885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>玩法说明</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集焊锡（游戏货币）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将电子元件焊接成防御塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制防御，抵御越来越强的病毒波</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性地管理升级与布局</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/9f91493259fec9e817f18375827d8a32.poster.avif?t=1757460885\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/9f91493259fec9e817f18375827d8a32.webm?t=1757460885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/9f91493259fec9e817f18375827d8a32.mp4?t=1757460885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔧 <strong>元件——你的防御塔</strong><br>每个防御塔都基于真实电子元件，并具有独特功能：<br>🟢 <strong>二极管</strong> – 对地面病毒快速射击<br>🔵 <strong>电容器</strong> – 高伤害炮塔，但射速慢<br>🔴 <strong>电感器</strong> – 持续低伤害激光，减速病毒<br>🟣 <strong>晶体管</strong> – 有效的空中防御<br>🟠 <strong>电阻器</strong> – 减缓病毒速度，但会损耗耐久度<br>💣 <strong>保险丝</strong> – 强力爆炸陷阱<br>⚙️ <strong>振荡器</strong> – 产生更多焊锡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/cdb3e5ba61f77fc2a1e2b32b3e073f6b.avif?t=1757460885\" width=1000 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☣️ <strong>病毒种类</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>普通病毒</strong> – 快速且数量多</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>间谍软件</strong> – 会飞但很脆弱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>广告软件</strong> – 会飞并对防御塔造成破坏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蠕虫</strong> – 感染并暂时禁用防御塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>木马</strong> – 地面坦克，被摧毁时分裂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>僵尸网络</strong> – Boss！巨型坦克，攻击防御塔</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165560/extras/76a31973d653a70ef027dbc6916d8aa2.avif?t=1757460885\" width=1000 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ <strong>进化与策略</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用焊锡进行升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集电池以解锁铜、银、金等级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次升级都会改变防御塔外观并获得新能力！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>关卡战役</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据表现解锁新关卡：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第1关到达第25波可解锁第2关</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每关带来新的挑战和独特目标</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 <strong>与众不同的塔防</strong><br>具有复古电子风格、沉浸式配乐和逐步升级的挑战，<i>Motherboard Under Attack</i> 是想要创意与原创体验的塔防迷的完美选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔻 将其加入愿望单，准备不惜一切保护主板！<br>💥 处理器指望你！</p>",
